rect with certainty: 'እርብቃ', 'ፉዋፍዋቴ', and 'የፎፋን'. These words did not correspond to known Amharic dictionary entries or common usage, and no clear, certain correction could be made. Loanwords like 'ብሊንድን' and 'ኢንሂል' were identified and processed as transliterations. Proper nouns such as 'ሮጆን' and 'የበጌምድርን' were also identified and their roots extracted. All remaining words were successfully lemmatized, translated, and tagged with their appropriate part of speech, adhering to the strict single-category rule for POS tagging. No single-character words were included in the final dataset.","input_words":["ታበላሻለህ","እርብቃ","መሸተኛነቱና","ሴሰኛነቱ","አሸበር","እንዲወስዱአቸው","ፉዋፍዋቴ","አይፈቀርም","ያስተዋወቅህበት","የጠቀስህበትን","ትጥሩ","ያለተፅዕኖና","አጸፋን","ሳይከፋት","የፎፋን","የሳኒቴንሽና","ተጋጣሚዎቼ","የተወዳደርን","የምንከትትበት","ብሊንድን","ሮጆን","ኢንሂል","ሊፈለቅቅ","አርማጌዶናዊ","ያቅማማል","የበጌምድርን","እየተሸለጉ","ሳንጠብቅና","ሰለጥንና","የኤርትራዊያንን"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"}]